Class HashTable<T extends PersonInterface>

  • java.lang.Object
    • HashTable<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HashTableInterface<T>

    public class HashTable<T extends PersonInterface>
extends java.lang.Object
implements HashTableInterface<T>
    This class provides a hash table used to store Person objects in an address book utility The hash table is implemented as an array of LinkedLists that contain PersonInterface objects Uses buckets to store objects with the same hash code
    Author:
    Adam Holt
